          text: 'GDPR penalty ceiling: 4% of global turnover. For a company with EUR 10B revenue, that is EUR 400M per incident. The cost of deploying quantum-certified anonymization across all PII processing pipelines is a rounding error by comparison. Patent 1 converts a recurring compliance liability into a one-time engineering project.',
