          'This ranking directly informs Zipminator\'s go-to-market sequence. The first customers will be Norwegian defense and intelligence (PST, E-tjenesten, FFI, Kongsberg Defence), because QDaria is the only domestic PQC vendor and Norwegian procurement rules favor domestic suppliers for classified systems. The second wave will be Norwegian financial institutions (DNB, SpareBank 1, Nordea, Norges Bank), driven by DORA enforcement. The third wave will be Nordic healthcare (Helse Sor-Ost, Helse Vest, Karolinska), driven by GDPR Article 9 and national health data laws. Enterprise SaaS and consumer adoption follow as PQC requirements cascade from regulated end-users to their software supply chains. The urgency ranking is a revenue timeline.',
