      'Twelve sectors, one shared cryptographic infrastructure. The use case map is not a wish list; it is a prioritized revenue pipeline driven by regulatory deadlines, adversary capabilities, and data lifetime requirements. Intelligence and defense agencies will adopt first because they face the most immediate threat and the hardest regulatory mandates. Financial institutions follow within months because DORA enforcement is live and penalty exposure is measured in billions. Healthcare systems adopt in parallel because patient data lifetimes exceed 30 years and HIPAA Safe Harbor compliance maps directly to Zipminator\'s anonymization engine. Telecom operators and IoT chipmakers represent the largest volume opportunity through Patent 2\'s per-device licensing model. Enterprise SaaS vendors adopt when their regulated customers make PQC a procurement requirement.',
